WEBVTT

00:12:59.958 --> 00:13:05.389
ne smeju nas prevariti
prividi racionalnosti.

00:13:05.413 --> 00:13:07.182
Moramo da sagledamo stvari iznutra,

00:13:07.206 --> 00:13:10.007
a tamo ćemo pronaći ekstremizam.

00:13:10.991 --> 00:13:12.977
Drugo,

00:13:13.001 --> 00:13:19.082
moramo shvatiti da istina nije relativna.

00:13:21.137 --> 00:13:22.601
Kao treće,

00:13:22.625 --> 00:13:26.314
moramo krenuti u napad,

00:13:26.338 --> 00:13:28.111
a ne u odbranu.

00:13:28.676 --> 00:13:31.283
Kada neko iznese nečuvenu tvrdnju,